      skos:note "Picking discovery as the near-term focus sequences the onboarding and governance use cases rather than sacrificing them. Discovery is the entry engagement; onboarding and governance follow as expansion and subscription in a single-customer arc. This is the key strategic logic for why the discovery wedge does not foreclose the other use cases." ;
      narr:supports narr:Narrative_DiscoveryOnboardingGovernanceSalesArc .

    narr:Claim_OrgMemoryDemotedSubUseCase a narr:Claim ;
      narr:aboutNode narr:Narrative_OrgMemoryDemotedToGovernanceSub ;
